transbit.tbits.common
Interface PropertiesEnum

All Known Implementing Classes:
DataSourcePool, DHJob, TBitsAppender, TBitsLogger
public interface PropertiesEnum

This class has the list of keys for the database related properties, which the DataSourcePool will look for in the properties file through the PropertiesHandler for using DataSourcePool as a static factory of connections.
